ZH: 今天我要去参加面试。
EN: I have a job interview today.

ZH: 这是我第一次参加面试。
EN: This is my first time attending an interview.

ZH: 面试的时间是下周三。
EN: The interview is scheduled for next Wednesday.

ZH: 我很紧张因为要面试一个非常重要的工作。
EN: I am very nervous because I have to interview for a very important job.

ZH: 面试的地点在公司总部。
EN: The interview will take place at the company headquarters.

ZH: 面试过程会持续多久？
EN: How long will the interview process last?

ZH: 面试官看起来很友好。
EN: The interviewer seems very friendly.

ZH: 我正在准备面试的自我介绍。
EN: I am preparing my self-introduction for the interview.

ZH: 面试时要注意穿着得体。
EN: Dress appropriately for the interview.

ZH: 面试结束后会有结果通知吗？
EN: Will there be a notification after the interview?

ZH: 我希望能在面试中表现出色。
EN: I hope to perform well in the interview.

ZH: 面试问题有点难，但我会尽力回答。
EN: The interview questions are a bit difficult, but I will do my best to answer them.

ZH: 面试的过程中要展现出自信。
EN: Show confidence during the interview.

ZH: 面试官问了我一些技术性的问题。
EN: The interviewer asked me some technical questions.

ZH: 面试的环境很正式。
EN: The interview environment is very formal.

ZH: 面试前先做些准备很重要。
EN: It is important to prepare before the interview.

ZH: 面试的结果直接影响我未来的职业发展。
EN: The outcome of the interview directly affects my future career development.

ZH: 面试结束后要发一封感谢信。
EN: Send a thank you note after the interview.

ZH: 面试的经验对我会很有帮助。
EN: The interview experience will be very helpful for me.

ZH: 我得抓住这次面试的机会。
EN: I have to seize this opportunity for the interview.
